OL,5, On a scorching June night, Bhagwan     
OL,6, Ghukse woke up with a jolt and decided 
OL,7, to run for his life.                   
OL,9,FFor the past month, Mr Ghukse had been 
OL,10,Fkept captive in a squalid shanty in the
OL,11,Fwestern state of Maharashtra along with
OL,12,Fsix other daily-wage workers. The      
OL,13,Fworkers were hired by some contractors 
OL,14,Fin the state's Osmanabad district to   
OL,15,Fdig wells, but were later forced into  
OL,16,Fbonded labour which is illegal in      
OL,17,FIndia.                                 
